org.coliper.ibean.extension

Interface LazyInit

  • All Superinterfaces:
    LazyInitChild, LazyInitParent

    public interface LazyInit
extends LazyInitChild, LazyInitParent
    Extension interface that supports with on-the-fly creation of nested IBeans. Beans of this type act as a LazyInitChild as well as a LazyInitParent. See LazyInitChild for a description and comparison of the lazy loading extension interfaces.
